Build a POC for PAAM using Lightning Web Components and Salesforce Lightning Design System. The POC should demonstrate the basic UI structure, reusable LWC components, SLDS styling, and key screen layout needed for the PAAM functionality. This will help validate the approach before moving forward with full development.

Acceptance Criteria:

Create a new LWC component for the PAAM POC.
UI should follow Salesforce Lightning Design System standards.
Page should include the basic PAAM layout and required sections.
Component should be responsive and display properly in Salesforce Lightning.
